{"tid":1333892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"資科辦公布智慧燈柱功能設備清單　將上載資料一線通網站供查閱","createTime":"2019-07-20T02:02:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T16:56:55.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6214493bbb54554656606cfdeddcb636bc4b871a","tid":1333892,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:02:08.000Z","msg":"有市民擔憂政府安裝的智慧燈柱有監控功能，侵犯私隱，資科辦繼日前宣布暫緩啟動3項有私隱憂慮的功能，今日（19日）再公布50支已安裝的智慧燈柱清單。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">該50支智慧燈柱設於九龍灣常悅道、啟德承啟道和觀塘市中心。</span>清單上列明燈柱位置、路段、已安裝的鏡頭和探測器，以及功能應用，資科辦希望讓公眾對智慧燈柱的功能及應用，有更深入客觀的理解。<br />\n<br />\n資科辦亦會在<span style=\"color: red;\">下星期內</span>通過資料一線通（<a href=\"http://data.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdata.gov.hk&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83J0VeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=0553b1cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">data.gov.hk</a>) 以開放數據形式發放智慧燈柱的位置及已啟動的功能，而日後每安裝新一批燈柱或新增功能，亦會以同樣高透明度發放資訊。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2406112/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2406112%2F&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83J0VeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=91c78f5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2406112/</a><br />\n全部燈柱嘅位置下星期先發放<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09350101572bbab095463a1d1795166aa833951","tid":1333892,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:12:02.000Z","msg":"宣布<span style=\"color: red;\">暫緩</span>啟動<br />\n<br />\n又暫緩 ?"},{"pid":"35e99cc97b5471f54c751d0d418b7ad7a5515cc3","tid":1333892,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a09350101572bbab095463a1d1795166aa833951","tid":1333892,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:12:02.000Z","msg":"宣布<span style=\"color: red;\">暫緩</span>啟動<br />\n<br />\n又暫緩 ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:17:31.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">enabled=0</code></pre>"},{"pid":"9123efda9